# Add, edit, and delete a supplier contact

## Add a supplier contact

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Suppliers/Supplier Contact** tab.
2. Click the **Add** button.
3. Fill in the required Supplier Contact details.
4. Click **Publish** to save and add the Supplier Contact.

## Edit a supplier contact

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, go to the **Suppliers/Supplier Contact** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the Supplier Contact you want to edit.
3. Make the necessary changes to the Supplier Contact details.
4. Click **Publish** to save your changes.

## Delete a supplier contact

1. In the left-hand navigation bar, select the **Suppliers/Supplier Contact** tab.
2. Double-click on the row of the Supplier Contact you want to delete.
3. Click the **Delete** button in the top-right corner of the screen.
4. In the confirmation popup, click **Confirm** to finalize the deletion.